                              <condition key="good">
                                The book is stained along the margins with humidity and dirt. The sewing has been repaired using a thread of vegetal origin in order to reinforce the original one
                                of animal origin. The lower board has been repaired joining together two different kinds of wood thanks to vegetal thread. The two parts don't match perfectly along the fracture.
                                The leather that covers the spine and part of the boards seems to have been added later as reparation intervention.
                              </condition>

